Project: Cocktail API Microservice

Supported TheCocktailDB Endpoints:
  • Search by name:           /search.php?s={name}
  • Search by first letter:   /search.php?f={letter}
  • Lookup by ID:             /lookup.php?i={id}
  • Random cocktail:          /random.php
  • Filter by ingredient:     /filter.php?i={ingredient}
  • Filter by category:       /filter.php?c={category}
  • Filter by glass:          /filter.php?g={glass}
  • List categories:          /list.php?c=list
  • List glasses:             /list.php?g=list
  • List ingredients:         /list.php?i=list
  • List alcoholic filters:   /list.php?a=list

Structure:

cocktail-service/src/main/java/pl/barmate/cocktails
    ├── CocktailApiApplication.java
    ├── config/RestClientConfig.java
    ├── controller/CocktailController.java
    ├── exception/NotFoundException.java
    ├── exception/GlobalExceptionHandler.java
    ├── model/ApiResponse.java
    ├── model/BriefCocktail.java
    ├── model/Cocktail.java
    ├── model/CocktailDeserializer.java
    ├── model/CocktailDto.java
    └── service/CocktailService.java
